The paper deals with information extraction from document images using deep learning techniques, which falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of natural language processing techniques for querying the extracted information, which falls under the domains of information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also mentions the use of relational schema and SQL queries for extracting information, which falls under the domain of machine learning (cs.LG).
